sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin as 管理员(web)
    participant H as Handler.ExtendUser<br/>(admin/users.go)
    participant M as models<br/>(quotas 表)
    participant A as audit_logs

    Note over Admin,H: 流程一：管理员提交延期（可带 reset_token_stats）
    Admin->>H: POST /admin/api/users/{id}/extend<br/>{days|until, reset_token_stats}
    H->>M: GetUserByID(id) 校验存在 & 非 admin
    H->>M: ExtendUserExpiry(id, newExpiresAt)<br/>UPDATE users SET expires_at=?, status='active'
    alt reset_token_stats == true
        H->>M: ResetTokenStats(id, now)<br/>清零 quota_token_5h_used / quota_token_week_used / quota_token_total_used<br/>bump week_start=now, month_start=now<br/>（绝不触碰 window_start / quota_5h_used / quota_total_used）
        H->>A: INSERT token_stats_reset<br/>{dimensions:["5h","week","month"], trigger:"extend", operator}
    end
    H->>A: INSERT extend（既有）<br/>detail: expires_at 旧→新
    H-->>Admin: 200 {expires_at, message:"有效期已更新至 …"}

    Note over Admin,H: 处于 429 的用户：下次请求即被 gate 放行（used 已=0，无需重启进程）

    Note over Admin,M: 流程二：网关请求时 gate 月窗口惰性重置（滚动 30 天）
    actor Client as 终端用户
    participant C as quota.Checker.CheckAndDeduct
    Client->>C: 请求（effectiveCalls）
    C->>M: AtomicDeductQuota(db, userID, effectiveCalls)
    M->>M: 单条原子 UPDATE<br/>SET quota_token_total_used = CASE WHEN month_start < (now-30d) THEN 0 ELSE quota_token_total_used END,<br/>    month_start        = CASE WHEN month_start < (now-30d) THEN now ELSE month_start END<br/>WHERE (quota_token_total_limit=0 OR (CASE WHEN month_start < (now-30d) THEN 0 ELSE quota_token_total_used END) < quota_token_total_limit)<br/>  AND quota_5h_used+?<=quota_5h_limit<br/>  AND quota_total_used+?<=quota_total_limit<br/>  AND (quota_token_5h_limit=0 OR quota_token_5h_used<quota_token_5h_limit)<br/>  AND (quota_token_week_limit=0 OR (CASE WHEN week_start < (now-7d) THEN 0 ELSE quota_token_week_used END) < quota_token_week_limit)
    Note right of M: 5h Token 维度：闸门【不】惰性重置，仅由 cron（Reset5hQuota/CompensateQuotaReset）<br/>每 5h 随 window_start 一并清零 quota_token_5h_used（沿用 PR #27 复用 window_start）
    M-->>C: rowsAffected==1 ? true : false（429 则 false）
